    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错。具体流程是：先在main上有个初始commit，然后切到newbranch做两次commit，其中第二次要标记为\"Pick me\"，因为这是要被cherry-pick的。之后切回main再做一次commit，然后再cherry-pick那个\"Pick me\"提交。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "newbranch",
