    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "明白了，我来画一下：从main开始，分支到newbranch，在那边做两次commit，第二次标记\"Pick me\"。然后main继续一个commit，再cherry-pick那个特定提交，最后merge newbranch。方向用BT（从下往上）比较清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
        "newbranch",
        "Pick me",
        "checkout",
        "commit",
