    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，我需要确认一下newbranch在cherry-pick之后的状态。cherry-pick是在main上操作，不会影响newbranch本身，所以最后merge的时候newbranch应该还是完整的两个commit对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "newbranch",
