        "cherry-pick",
        "merge"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，cherry-pick只在main上创建一个新的提交，内容是复制\"Pick me\"的变更。newbranch保持原样，所以最后merge newbranch会把它的两个commit都带进来。这样main上会有那个cherry-pick产生的提交，以及merge产生的合并提交。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "main",
